Package algorithms.mazeGenerators

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CellSelection
    This interface define the way we choose the next cell in growing tree algorithm
    Maze3dGenerator
    This interface is used define the maze generators behavior.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GrowingTreeGenerator
    This class is the GrowingTree algorithm to generate a maze.
    Maze3d
    This class defines a 3D Maze in a real world.
    Maze3dGeneratorAbstract
    This abstract class is used as a common class to maze generators.
    newestCell
    This class Implements selection of cell of the newest cell in a list.
    Position
    This class Defines a Position in 3D maze in real world.
    randomCell
    This class Implements selection of cell of random cell in a List.
    SimpleMaze3dGenerator
    This class is the SimpleMaze algorithm to generate a maze.
